{
  "stem": "4670.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the company felt that it was not unusual to hire a chauffeur for the people that were working for them, especially if they had to travel, because they felt it was a waste for the director to drive and have to worry about a car.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had a chauffeur, which he was not for our family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was just for my dad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had this man for years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then something happened and we needed a new chauffeur.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had hired this man who had come to our house and picked up my dad and had been with us-- I don't know-- a couple of months or so.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And began to make anti-Jewish remarks, and very nasty remarks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my dad decided to fire him because he felt he couldn't use him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that point, he came to work the very next day with a revolver and he tried to kill my dad.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And luckily, some of the agents were there and they grabbed the gun and they got rid of him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it drove home some fear to us, which we had not expected.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And pretty soon after that, when Hitler was more established, was in 1932, was just before he became chancellor, the situation changed completely.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Phoenix Company, who were very pleased with my dad, had to let him go because he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Jews were not allowed in positions anymore at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were beginning to remove the Jewish people from all corporate offices and other important positions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The company liked my dad so well, they paid him one year severance pay, which was very unusual.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At that point, the physicians could no longer practice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Lawyers could no longer practice.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
